       <div id="c29430" class="csc-default"> 
        <!--  Header: [begin] --> 
        <div class="csc-header csc-header-n1">
         <h1 class="csc-firstHeader">London Hopper 2017</h1>
        </div> 
        <!--  Header: [end] --> 
       </div> 
       <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:29430/text [end] --> 
       <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:29644/textpic [begin] --> 
       <div id="c29644" class="csc-frame csc-frame-rulerAfter"> 
        <!--  Image block: [begin] --> 
        <div class="csc-textpic csc-textpic-intext-right">
         <div class="csc-textpic-imagewrap">
          <div class="csc-textpic-image csc-textpic-last">
           <img src="fileadmin/_processed_/csm_pic_group_2444b1e78e.jpg" width="220" height="165" alt="" border="0">
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="csc-textpic-text"> 
          <!--  Text: [begin] --> 
          <h2><a href="http://academy.bcs.org/content/london-hopper-colloquium-2017" title="Opens external link in new window" target="_top" class="external-link-new-window">Booking is now open for London Hopper:&nbsp;Thursday 25 May</a></h2> 
          <p class="align-justify">UCL and BCS Academy will be presenting the 13th London Hopper Colloquium on Thursday 25 May 2017 at the BCS headquarters in London. This year you will hear women speakers talk about their work on building rehabilitation technologies, cybersecurity, simulations of the human heart, and infrastructure for smart cities.</p> 
          <p class="align-justify">London Hopper is an annual 1-day event for researchers across the UK who are building a career in computing. As well as women speakers talking about their research, it will feature &nbsp;a spotlight competition with cash prizes open to postgraduate students, and lots of opportunities to meet and network with other&nbsp;early career&nbsp;researchers in computing.&nbsp;</p> 
          <p class="align-justify">The event is free but you must book. Booking will be available via the BCS website <a href="http://academy.bcs.org/content/london-hopper-colloquium-2017" title="Opens external link in new window" target="_top" class="external-link-new-window">here</a>.</p> 
          <p><i>Note: &nbsp;We have a new speaker in the&nbsp;14:45 - 15:15 time slot.</i></p> 
          <!--  Text: [end] --> 
         </div>
        </div> 
        <!--  Image block: [end] --> 
       </div> 
